videos.description: Darrell Bowie drives to the bucket, hits the shot and is fouled. He would miss the free throw.
videos.headline: Iowa State's Bowie drives to the basket for the bucket

videos.description: Iowa State's Deonte Burton steals the ball and drives the lane for the and-1.
videos.headline: Iowa State's Burton turns defense into offense

videos.description: Iowa State's Deonte Burton steals the ball and soars for the one-handed dunk.
videos.headline: Iowa State's Burton finishes with a huge one-handed slam

videos.description: 1H (4:34) ISU Matt Thomas made Three Point Jumper.
videos.headline: M. Thomas drains the fast break 3-pointer from way downtown

videos.description: Indiana State's Brenton Scott makes a 3-pointer from long distance to put the Sycamores up 58-56 over Iowa State.
videos.headline: Scott puts Indiana State back in the lead with a big 3-pointer

videos.description: Iowa State's Nazareth Mitrou-Long spins around a defender and goes baseline for the layup to pull the Cyclones within one of Indiana State.
videos.headline: Iowa State's Mitrou-Long with a sweet spin move for a layup

videos.description: Iowa State's Monte Morris makes a nifty, driving layup late in the Cyclone's game against the Indiana State.
videos.headline: Morris goes up and under to tie the game

videos.description: Iowa State's Matt Thomas gets the friendly roll on the corner 3-pointer to give the Cyclones a 72-71 lead over Indiana State.
videos.headline: Iowa State's Thomas gets the friendly roll to take the lead late
